36
00:04:11,670 --> 00:04:13,380
♫ Fantasizing about a sky with you and I ♫

37
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:15,940
Ruoxi, you have made Minmin

38
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:18,060
metamorphosize into a new star of the grasslands.

39
