♫ The northern wind keeps blowing ♫

75
00:07:14,780 --> 00:07:15,740
Not bad. Not bad.

76
00:07:15,740 --> 00:07:17,340
Ruoxi, come here.

77
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:19,740
Summoning Ruoxi!

78
00:07:26,620 --> 00:07:28,220
Your Majesty.

79
00:07:28,220 --> 00:07:29,580
What a wonderful performance.

80
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:31,280
I was captivated by it.

81
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,940
If I had known you had such an ability,

82
00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:36,640
I would have let you handle all the palace performances.

83
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:38,540
Your servant only have this bit of ability.

84
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:40,440
It's only some lowly skill; and

85
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:42,040
has already exhausted my limited abilities.

86
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:44,400
Your Imperial Majesty, therefore, should not make things difficult for your servant.

87
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:45,980
Tonight's dance performance

88
00:07:45,980 --> 00:07:49,160
is so lovely. It was all due to Minmin.

89
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,680
Min'min Ge'Ge.
(Princess Minmin)

90
00:07:53,980 --> 00:07:55,900
Your Imperial Majesty.

91
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:58,180
I just saw that your long sleeve weaving,

92
00:07:58,180 --> 00:07:59,620
ribbon-like, floating and dancing,

93
00:07:59,620 --> 00:08:02,600
your body bending in the wind, similar to a willow tree,

94
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,740
reminded me of a lotus flower rising above green water.

95
00:08:05,460 --> 00:08:08,020
I thought a goddess had descended from heaven.

96
00:08:08,020 --> 00:08:09,260
Your Imperial Majesty is exaggerating.

97
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,700
Reward her with the Jade Ruyi.

98
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:13,100
Yes, Sire.

99
00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:17,900
Thank you, Imperial Majesty.

100
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:24,180
I'd like to award something to Ruoxi.

101
00:08:25,140 --> 00:08:26,860
Hurry up and say thank you.

102
00:08:26,860 --> 00:08:28,340
Thank you, Your Highness.

103
00:08:33,140 --> 00:08:34,620
The exact same jade pendant.

104
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:37,060
Minmin has one as well

105
00:08:37,660 --> 00:08:38,780
Originally,

106
00:08:38,780 --> 00:08:40,739
Minmin had an older twin sister.

107
00:08:40,739 --> 00:08:42,100
After the two were born,

108
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:43,780
I could hardly contain my joy.

109
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:46,500
At the same time, I got a beautiful piece of jade

110
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:49,259
and ordered two jade pendant pieces to be made.

111
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:52,860
I never thought that before the pendants were finished

112
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:56,340
her sister would pass away.

113
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:00,280
This jade pendant

114
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:02,360
represents Wang Ye's feelings for his daughter.

115
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:04,060
I don't dare accept.

116
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:07,000
Since I gave it to you,

117
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,940
there is no daren't about it.

118
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:11,700
Then you should accept it.

119
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:13,140
Thank you, Wang Ye.

120
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:15,300
All right, get up. Get up.

121
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:17,120
Wang Ye, I'm tired.

122
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,680
Why don't we return, to rest?

123
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,100
Please.

124
00:09:21,740 --> 00:09:24,020
Crown Prince, I'll leave you in charge.

125
00:09:24,020 --> 00:09:25,000
Yes.

126
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:28,140
Walk well, Your Majesty.

127
00:09:32,620 --> 00:09:34,980
Come, serve the wine.

128
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:39,460
To send off Heshu and Zhoying,

129
00:09:39,460 --> 00:09:40,580
why don't we brothers

130
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:41,980
drink with them.

131
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:43,340
Thank you, Crown Prince.

132
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:48,420
Here, I'll toast you two.

133
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:50,940
Tonight, none of us will return home sober.

134
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:52,420
Here, cheers.

135
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:54,460
What are you thinking about?

136
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:58,180
Already, bright purple and passion pink bloom in profusion
(The Peony Pavilion)

137
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:00,300
Yet

138
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:02,460
such splendor is abandoned to crumbling, well-faded walls

139
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:06,380
But in this glorious season

140
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:11,580
where are the sounds of joy in this garden?

141
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:14,040
What are you talking about?

142
00:10:14,860 --> 00:10:18,500
It's nothing, I'm just sad.

143
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:20,300
Tomorrow, you will have to leave.

144
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:23,420
Happy times

145
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:25,320
are always too short.

146
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:28,340
I don't know when we will be able to meet again.

147
00:10:28,340 --> 00:10:30,500
I have a parting gift to give you.

148
00:10:31,740 --> 00:10:33,340
I promised you before.

149
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:34,660
What?

150
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,580
Crown Prince,

151
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:40,080
I want to play a song

152
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,680
for everyone.

153
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,300
Why not?

154
00:10:43,300 --> 00:10:44,780
All of us know

155
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:46,080
that your flute playing is good.

156
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,200
Tonight,

157
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:49,420
let us have the good fortune of listening to your flute.

158
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,280
I don't know why, but

159
00:12:30,820 --> 00:12:32,900
I suddenly want to go far, far away.

160
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:34,900
I want peace.

161
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:38,100
Others say

162
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:40,180
music is gradually fading and sound is disappearing,

163
00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:42,540
feeling too much is more troubling than not feeling.

164
00:12:44,220 --> 00:12:45,740
If people didn't have emotions,

165
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:49,060
then they can truly leave troubles behind.

166
00:12:53,020 --> 00:12:54,540
After a happy gathering

167
00:12:55,180 --> 00:12:57,660
I've always felt more deserted.

168
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:16,220
Do you think MinMin and Zuoying

169
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:18,640
have a possibility of being together?

170
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:20,020
4th Prince's meaning is...

171
00:13:21,460 --> 00:13:23,340
Last night, I saw that your eyes

172
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:25,420
kept looking at them.

173
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:28,980
I truly wish for them to be together.

174
00:13:30,100 --> 00:13:31,900
What does 4th Prince think?

175
00:13:33,060 --> 00:13:35,340
This Prince Zuoying has great ability,

176
00:13:35,340 --> 00:13:36,820
but because he was born of a commoner,

177
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:39,020
he isn't valued by Yinergenluo Wang Ye.

178
00:13:39,900 --> 00:13:41,900
Seeing Imperial Father this time

179
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:44,580
was not a particularly important task.

180
00:13:44,580 --> 00:13:46,300
So it was given to him.

181
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:50,100
But,

182
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:52,700
I thought this is good fortune born from misfortune.

183
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:55,520
I'm afraid in the future,

184
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:58,460
he will cause trouble for his father and brother.

185
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:01,680
Then is Minmin marrying Zuoying

186
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:03,680
the best choice?

187
00:14:04,940 --> 00:14:06,980
This is none of your business.

188
00:14:06,980 --> 00:14:08,900
You're just being a matchmaker.

189
00:14:11,380 --> 00:14:13,900
Are you willing to be by yourself your entire life?

190
00:14:15,340 --> 00:14:17,780
Don't say any nonsense like being filial.

191
00:14:21,180 --> 00:14:22,420
I'm too tired.

192
00:14:22,420 --> 00:14:23,900
These years in the palace

193
00:14:23,900 --> 00:14:25,360
are full of rules

194
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,480
and schemes.

195
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,380
Actions have to be thought through 3 times

196
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:31,620
and pondered on for 3 more times.

197
00:14:31,620 --> 00:14:33,500
But I am not that type of person.

198
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:36,380
I just want to go far away,

199
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:39,260
laugh when I want to,

200
00:14:39,260 --> 00:14:41,060
and cry when I want to.

201
00:14:42,300 --> 00:14:44,980
At this moment, marrying

202
00:14:44,980 --> 00:14:47,460
is trading the big cage of the Forbidden City

203
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:49,340
for a smaller cage.

204
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:52,280
I would be more well-regarded in the Forbidden City than after marriage.

205
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:53,540
So why should I marry?

206
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:57,120
Thinking of the fighting between wives after marriage,

207
00:14:57,120 --> 00:15:00,300
I think shaving my head and becoming a nun would be better.

208
00:15:02,260 --> 00:15:04,040
With your current status,

209
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:06,640
it is impossible for you to make that decision.

210
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:08,540
The more Imperial Father values you,

211
00:15:08,540 --> 00:15:10,700
the less you can control your marriage.

212
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:14,800
Take for example, Wang Ye giving you the jade pendant.

213
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:18,540
Wang Ye implied that he thought of you as a daughter.

214
00:15:19,020 --> 00:15:20,280
Minmin and her brother

215
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:22,340
treat you better than the Crown Prince.

216
00:15:23,340 --> 00:15:26,300
Although we don't know what Wang Ye's motives are,

217
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:28,740
when Imperial Father arranges your marriage

218
00:15:28,740 --> 00:15:32,280
it will have to be thought over very seriously.

219
00:15:32,280 --> 00:15:35,100
If you wish to be like the other palace maids

220
00:15:35,100 --> 00:15:37,140
and be released from the palace when your time is up,

221
00:15:37,700 --> 00:15:39,440
then let me advise you

222
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,000
to stop dreaming.

223
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,580
Why don't you think about

224
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:46,200
how to let Imperial Father

225
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,740
arrange a marriage

226
00:15:47,740 --> 00:15:49,220
that will make you satisfied?

227
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:52,760
If I don't want to marry,

228
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:54,800
then no one can force me.

229
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:56,620
Then you should prepare 3 meters of white cloth;
(To commit suicide)

230
00:15:57,940 --> 00:15:59,060
and harden your heart

231
00:15:59,060 --> 00:16:00,220
against caring that your death

232
00:16:00,220 --> 00:16:02,680
will cause trouble to your father and clan.

233
00:16:06,980 --> 00:16:09,340
The palace does not allow for dreams.

234
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:12,920
I advise you to wake up

235
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:15,120
and think of your next step.

236
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,520
When the matter finally comes,

237
00:16:17,220 --> 00:16:19,280
you won't be able to do anything.

238
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:21,320
Is not marrying really not a possibility?

239
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:23,300
I will not hurt anyone by not marrying,

240
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:25,100
so why do I still have to marry?

241
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,820
Do you not understand what I'm saying,

242
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:28,580
or is it that you don't want to understand?

243
00:16:29,900 --> 00:16:31,900
Imperial Father is the one to make the decision;

244
00:16:31,900 --> 00:16:33,300
you can only be obedient.

245
00:16:39,780 --> 00:16:41,480
Or is it that in your heart,

246
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:43,860
there is no one you want to marry?

247
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:49,980
Is there no one that you can be free with?

248
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:18,540
I saw a document that would make anyone angry.

249
00:17:18,540 --> 00:17:19,940
I sent

250
00:17:19,940 --> 00:17:22,340
money for the natural disaster victims of Fujian,

251
00:17:22,340 --> 00:17:24,740
but actually, the money was taken by my officials.

252
00:17:24,740 --> 00:17:27,100
So many people died of hunger.

253
00:17:27,100 --> 00:17:29,019
If there were no one backing them,

254
00:17:29,019 --> 00:17:30,580
how would the officials

255
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:32,720
dare to take such an action?

256
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:36,420
I love my people like my children,

257
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:37,660
but my servants

258
00:17:37,660 --> 00:17:40,540
see the people's money and food

259
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:42,060
as their own.

260
00:17:43,180 --> 00:17:46,260
I ordered 4th Prince to investigate the matter;

261
00:17:46,260 --> 00:17:49,160
and found that the officials of the Ministry of Revenue were also involved.

262
