00:29:45,624 --> 00:29:48,510
won't be able to continue to gain benefits.

530
00:29:48,510 --> 00:29:52,713
In that way, the Crown Prince won't be able to continue protecting his men without any scruples.

531
00:29:52,713 --> 00:29:55,381
4th Brother is providing assistance on the surface,

532
00:29:55,381 --> 00:29:57,489
but his actual role is keeping the Crown Prince in check.

533
00:29:57,489 --> 00:29:58,843
His job has been made so much easier and he still stands to gain.

534
00:30:00,106 --> 00:30:02,394
This drastic maneuver of 4th Brother

535
00:30:02,394 --> 00:30:04,514
is really a master stroke.

536
00:30:04,514 --> 00:30:07,843
I have to really hand it to him.

537
00:30:07,843 --> 00:30:10,105
However, I, on the other hand,

538
00:30:10,105 --> 00:30:12,330
really admire your thought process.

539
00:30:12,330 --> 00:30:15,065
Your thinking is more incisive than what I would have imagined.

540
00:30:15,065 --> 00:30:17,164
4th Brother's every movement,

541
00:30:17,164 --> 00:30:19,617
you know like the back of your hand.

542
00:30:19,617 --> 00:30:22,604
You're all intelligent people.

543
00:30:22,604 --> 00:30:26,859
Both of you are really intelligent but are on opposing sides.

544
00:30:26,859 --> 00:30:29,674
Too bad we were born into the royal family.

545
00:30:29,674 --> 00:30:31,908
Otherwise, if the two of you joined forces,

546
00:30:31,908 --> 00:30:33,555
in whatever matters arose,

547
00:30:33,555 --> 00:30:36,549
I believe success would be guaranteed.

548
00:30:38,178 --> 00:30:39,246
Eighth Brother,

549
00:30:39,246 --> 00:30:40,964
can you promise me one thing?

550
00:30:42,688 --> 00:30:44,983
If one day you are the ruler of the court,

551
00:30:44,983 --> 00:30:47,357
can you let 4th Brother retire quietly

552
00:30:47,357 --> 00:30:49,175
to lead a life of leisure away from all courtly affairs?

553
00:30:51,101 --> 00:30:55,877
If you ask 4th Brother the same question,

554
00:30:55,877 --> 00:30:59,620
what do you think his answer would be?

555
00:31:13,238 --> 00:31:15,957
9th Prince, this month,

556
00:31:15,957 --> 00:31:18,035
we hit the jackpot.

557
00:31:18,035 --> 00:31:19,850
The money everyone else is scared to accept

558
00:31:19,850 --> 00:31:22,726
has come to us now.

559
00:31:22,726 --> 00:31:24,037
Come on, everyone,

560
00:31:24,037 --> 00:31:27,063
let's toast to 9th Prince for this.

561
00:31:27,063 --> 00:31:28,867
Here, 9th, here.

562
00:31:28,867 --> 00:31:33,789
Cheers.

563
00:31:41,824 --> 00:31:44,213
You fellows listen to me carefully now.

564
00:31:44,213 --> 00:31:45,971
Starting from today,

565
00:31:45,971 --> 00:31:47,946
all of the summer bribes, winter bribes,

566
00:31:47,946 --> 00:31:49,375
and any other bribes...

567
00:31:49,375 --> 00:31:51,390
you must reject them all.

568
00:31:52,281 --> 00:31:54,573
9th Prince,

569
00:31:54,573 --> 00:31:57,288
how about we just be more careful about it?

570
00:31:57,288 --> 00:32:00,335
- That's right, that's right.
- The Crown Prince's men are accepting them too.

571
00:32:00,335 --> 00:32:02,968
If we end up getting caught,

572
00:32:02,968 --> 00:32:04,929
won't they...

573
00:32:04,929 --> 00:32:07,087
won't they also get in trouble?

574
00:32:07,087 --> 00:32:08,643
- That's true.
- Right?

575
00:32:08,643 --> 00:32:09,618
Even if it's death,

576
00:32:09,618 --> 00:32:11,290
it won't be on us alone.

577
00:32:11,290 --> 00:32:13,522
Is that correct?

578
00:32:13,522 --> 00:32:15,469
Then is what I'm saying wrong?

579
00:32:17,684 --> 00:32:19,170
That's not it, Ninth Prince.

580
00:32:19,170 --> 00:32:22,464
What I'm saying is, boldly tread in this world,

581
00:32:22,464 --> 00:32:24,957
instead of carefully inching along.

582
00:32:24,957 --> 00:32:27,111
Am I right, everybody?

583
00:32:27,111 --> 00:32:29,680
- Right, right, right!
-  You got that right!

584
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:34,254
The houses that the Crown Prince's men are living in are getting bigger and bigger, but what about us?

585
00:32:34,254 --> 00:32:35,740
We...

586
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:38,048
When we see the Crown Prince's men,

587
00:32:38,048 --> 00:32:42,419
- we don't dare to lift our heads up high.
- That's right!

588
00:32:42,419 --> 00:32:47,081
9th Prince, a skinny dog is an embarrassment to its owner.

589
00:32:47,081 --> 00:32:49,031
That's right, Ninth Prince.

590
00:32:49,031 --> 00:32:49,672
Are you done talking?

591
00:32:49,672 --> 00:32:54,316
Ninth Prince, we...

592
00:32:54,316 --> 00:32:56,038
All of you, get out!

593
00:32:56,038 --> 00:32:59,017
Get out!

594
00:32:59,017 --> 00:33:01,940
Let's go, go, go!

595
00:33:01,940 --> 00:33:04,476
Wretched slaves!

596
00:33:04,476 --> 00:33:09,284
Do you think that one account book can stop me!

597
00:33:09,284 --> 00:33:11,745
If it weren't for Eighth Prince,

598
00:33:11,745 --> 00:33:15,121
I wouldn't have you fellows looking down on me!

599
00:33:32,479 --> 00:33:35,087
Buns for sale.

600
00:33:35,087 --> 00:33:38,295
Hot steaming buns.

601
00:33:41,574 --> 00:33:43,271
Buns for sale.

602
00:33:43,271 --> 00:33:46,608
Fresh from the oven.

603
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:52,320
Buns for sale.

604
00:33:52,320 --> 00:33:55,270
Buns for sale.

605
00:33:55,270 --> 00:34:00,386
Fresh from the oven.

606
00:34:00,386 --> 00:34:02,840
Boss, come and buy two buns.

607
00:34:02,840 --> 00:34:04,858
All right.

608
00:34:12,417 --> 00:34:13,761
4th Brother, 13th Brother.

609
00:34:13,761 --> 00:34:15,243
No need to see me off.

610
00:34:15,243 --> 00:34:17,139
Godspeed, Crown Prince.

611
00:34:40,257 --> 00:34:42,614
9th Brother, since Imperial Father

612
00:34:42,614 --> 00:34:43,568
didn't say anything,

613
00:34:43,568 --> 00:34:44,456
then isn't that to say

614
00:34:44,456 --> 00:34:47,469
4th Brother didn't report everything he found out?

615
00:34:47,469 --> 00:34:48,816
So should I

616
00:34:48,816 --> 00:34:51,827
bow to him in gratitude?

617
00:34:51,827 --> 00:34:54,217
You are all afraid of him. I'm not!

618
00:34:54,217 --> 00:34:55,478
Ninth.

619
00:35:01,272 --> 00:35:03,180
8th Brother will handle the matter.

620
00:35:03,180 --> 00:35:04,905
Please don't create more trouble.

621
00:35:22,931 --> 00:35:25,717
Fourth Prince, it's done.

622
00:35:30,370 --> 00:35:34,216
Thirteenth, come and see Ninth's account.

623
00:35:36,863 --> 00:35:39,514
He still doesn't know how to cover up.

624
00:35:39,514 --> 00:35:42,282
What do we do?

625
00:35:42,282 --> 00:35:44,951
Arrange a meeting with 8th Brother.

626
00:35:58,313 --> 00:35:59,456
4th Brother.

627
00:35:59,456 --> 00:36:01,496
8th Brother.

628
00:36:01,496 --> 00:36:04,093
I'm returning this account book to you.

629
00:36:04,093 --> 00:36:06,215
Although 9th brother may sometimes do the wrong thing,

630
00:36:06,215 --> 00:36:08,165
he will learn his lesson in the end.

631
00:36:08,165 --> 00:36:10,223
He won't let you down.

632
00:36:11,143 --> 00:36:13,504
I have always thought that 9th Brother listens to you the most,

633
00:36:13,504 --> 00:36:15,962
but I realized I was wrong.

634
00:36:15,962 --> 00:36:17,748
9th Brother is obstinate and opinionated.

635
00:36:17,748 --> 00:36:19,163
He has an unbending nature.

636
00:36:19,163 --> 00:36:21,392
In whatever he does, he doesn't think about the consequences.

637
00:36:22,204 --> 00:36:24,001
If he has offended you in any way,

638
00:36:24,001 --> 00:36:26,184
please allow me to act on his behalf

639
00:36:26,184 --> 00:36:29,317
and apologize to you.

640
00:36:29,317 --> 00:36:30,796
Before yesterday,

641
00:36:30,796 --> 00:36:33,025
I wanted to let bygones be bygones,

642
00:36:33,025 --> 00:36:34,325
but now I've encountered

643
00:36:34,325 --> 00:36:35,533
an even trickier problem.

644
00:36:35,533 --> 00:36:37,576
I hope to get some suggestions from you.

645
00:36:38,651 --> 00:36:41,020
If Fourth Brother can't deal with this difficult problem,

646
00:36:41,020 --> 00:36:44,638
I think I'll be of no help to you.

647
00:36:44,638 --> 00:36:45,914
Bring the accounts over.

648
00:36:45,914 --> 00:36:48,072
Yes.

649
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:13,215
Is this the difficult problem that 4th Brother was referring to?

650
00:37:13,215 --> 00:37:17,295
I can't compare with 4th Brother, in regards to taking charge.

651
00:37:17,295 --> 00:37:19,774
May I ask you something?

652
00:37:19,774 --> 00:37:21,478
4th Brother, have you only investigated

653
00:37:21,478 --> 00:37:24,257
9th Brother's muddled accounts?

654
00:37:24,257 --> 00:37:26,150
8th Brother, you're the kind that understands

655
00:37:26,150 --> 00:37:28,776
that I do what I have to do.

656
00:37:28,776 --> 00:37:30,480
Imperial Father has ordered a thorough investigation.

657
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:32,609
Everyone in court has exercised restraint,

658
00:37:32,609 --> 00:37:34,070
including the Crown Prince.

659
00:37:35,185 --> 00:37:36,950
Only 9th Brother hasn't.

660
00:37:43,289 --> 00:37:45,871
4th Brother has the Imperial order.

661
00:37:45,871 --> 00:37:50,208
However you need to handle it, you'll handle it.

662
00:37:55,542 --> 00:37:56,570
I just don't believe

663
00:37:56,570 --> 00:37:58,449
Old Fourth can do whatever he wants with me!

664
00:37:58,449 --> 00:38:00,796
Don't think just because he's got the Crown Prince  supporting him,

665
00:38:00,796 --> 00:38:04,140
he can do whatever he wants and disregard everyone else!

666
00:38:09,504 --> 00:38:11,663
Are you all mute?

667
00:38:15,988 --> 00:38:18,685
Eighth Brother, what should I do?

668
00:38:18,685 --> 00:38:19,999
Tell me what to do.

669
00:38:22,252 --> 00:38:23,552
If you want me to get rid of 4th Brother,

670
00:38:23,552 --> 00:38:26,631
I will go out right now with a knife!

671
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:34,442
Eighth Brother, say something.

672
00:38:43,378 --> 00:38:46,097
14th, I know that

673
00:38:46,097 --> 00:38:47,694
4th and you have the same mother.

674
00:38:47,694 --> 00:38:49,233
You won't say anything.

675
00:38:49,233 --> 00:38:50,712
But think about it,

676
00:38:50,712 --> 00:38:51,648
does 4th consider you

677
00:38:51,648 --> 00:38:53,699
to be that close?

678
00:39:02,288 --> 00:39:04,892
10th, you usually don't have an opinion.

679
00:39:04,892 --> 00:39:05,961
But today,

680
00:39:05,961 --> 00:39:07,593
no matter what, you must say something!

681
00:39:07,593 --> 00:39:08,954
What do you think I should do?

682
00:39:12,305 --> 00:39:14,652
9th Brother, I'm not criticizing you.

683
00:39:14,652 --> 00:39:16,517
8th Brother asked you earlier on to stop.

684
00:39:16,517 --> 00:39:17,896
But you didn't listen.

685
00:39:17,896 --> 00:39:20,153
And 4th brother gave 8th brother another document.

686
00:39:20,153 --> 00:39:23,383
If you're not criticizing me, what are you doing right now?!

687
00:39:27,500 --> 00:39:28,777
8th Brother.

688
00:39:28,777 --> 00:39:32,465
Is there any other way?

689
00:39:32,465 --> 00:39:34,126
I've already asked 4th brother

690
00:39:34,126 --> 00:39:37,756
to deliver the accounts to our Imperial Father.

691
00:39:37,756 --> 00:39:40,524
8th brother, what are you saying?

692
00:39:40,524 --> 00:39:42,175
I've done all I can.

693
00:39:42,175 --> 00:39:43,707
You've done your best?

694
00:39:43,707 --> 00:39:45,343
This is called doing your best!

695
00:39:45,343 --> 00:39:46,951
I see you're doing your best to save yourself!

696
00:39:46,951 --> 00:39:48,222
9th Brother.

697
00:39:48,222 --> 00:39:49,877
How can you say that to 8th Brother?

698
00:39:49,877 --> 00:39:53,395
Am I wrong?!

699
00:39:53,395 --> 00:39:56,641
Yes! I have only myself to blame!

700
00:39:56,641 --> 00:39:58,986
I thought that

701
00:39:58,986 --> 00:40:01,029
we were all in the same boat.

702
00:40:01,029 --> 00:40:04,373
But before the storm comes, everyone has already abandoned the ship!

703
00:40:04,373 --> 00:40:06,602
Fine! Don't worry.

704
00:40:06,602 --> 00:40:08,831
No matter what Imperial Father will do to me,

705
00:40:08,831 --> 00:40:11,037
I won't let any of you be implicated!

706
00:40:11,037 --> 00:40:12,291
Calm down!

707
00:40:12,291 --> 00:40:13,824
How do you want me to calm down?!

708
00:40:13,824 --> 00:40:14,845
Think about it.

709
00:40:14,845 --> 00:40:17,074
What would you do if you were 8th Brother?

710
00:40:17,074 --> 00:40:19,211
Even if 8th Brother asks 4th Brother to cover up,

711
00:40:19,211 --> 00:40:21,161
4th Brother might not do it.

712
00:40:21,161 --> 00:40:23,065
In the end, he will have to suffer people's gossip.

713
00:40:23,065 --> 00:40:24,040
8th Brother,

714
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:25,526
you have really miscalculated your move.

715
00:40:25,526 --> 00:40:27,913
If only at that time the account books had been burnt to ashes,

716
00:40:27,913 --> 00:40:29,567
then 4th Brother wouldn't have had any evidence.

717
00:40:29,567 --> 00:40:32,346
10th, just go home.

718
00:40:32,346 --> 00:40:33,400
How come when I hear you speaking,

719
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:35,568
it sounds so dumb?

720
00:40:35,568 --> 00:40:36,983
What do you mean?

721
00:40:36,983 --> 00:40:38,808
I'm thinking on your behalf.

722
00:40:38,808 --> 00:40:40,269
If you are thinking on my behalf,

723
00:40:40,269 --> 00:40:41,362
then please first go home

724
00:40:41,362 --> 00:40:42,356
and bring back your brain!

725
00:40:42,356 --> 00:40:44,556
Then think again about a way to help me!

726
00:40:44,556 --> 00:40:46,624
Your words sound so awful.

727
00:40:46,624 --> 00:40:48,453
At home, I suffer with Ming Yu's temper!

728
00:40:48,453 --> 00:40:50,109
Now I have to suffer with yours!

729
00:40:50,109 --> 00:40:50,824
I...

730
00:40:50,824 --> 00:40:52,231
Was I born to suffer from both your tempers?

731
00:40:52,231 --> 00:40:53,692
Stop arguing!

732
00:40:56,479 --> 00:40:58,218
No matter what.

733
00:40:58,218 --> 00:41:00,262
I'm a man.

734
00:41:00,262 --> 00:41:02,423
I will follow through with what I said.

735
00:41:02,423 --> 00:41:04,813
- You--
- Don't worry.

736
00:41:04,813 --> 00:41:07,453
As long as that corrupt Crown Prince is still around,

737
00:41:07,453 --> 00:41:09,378
even if I have to die,

738
00:41:09,378 --> 00:41:10,318
he will fall right along with me.

739
00:41:16,290 --> 00:41:17,887
The Crown Prince's men

740
00:41:17,887 --> 00:41:19,806
have already curbed their excesses.

741
00:41:21,234 --> 00:41:23,158
You don't need to panic about losing your head.

742
00:41:23,158 --> 00:41:27,663
Imperial Father won't do anything to you.

743
00:41:54,505 --> 00:41:56,981
So these are the so-called Pillars of the State,

744
00:41:58,288 --> 00:42:01,585
the country's foundations.

745
00:42:08,098 --> 00:42:12,724
This incident is thus concluded.

746
00:42:12,724 --> 00:42:16,085
The people involved in this case are exempted from questioning.

747
00:42:16,900 --> 00:42:19,536
Their sentence will be limited to making compensation.

748
00:42:22,332 --> 00:42:23,948
Everyone is dismissed!

749
00:42:24,680 --> 00:42:26,061
I will take my leave.

750
00:42:26,061 --> 00:42:28,072
- We will take our leave.
- We will take our leave.

751
00:42:58,499 --> 00:43:02,888
Ruoxi, come up.

752
00:43:11,636 --> 00:43:13,873
Greetings 4th Prince, greetings 13th Prince.

753
00:43:13,873 --> 00:43:15,171
Rise.

754
00:43:18,620 --> 00:43:21,371
Why aren't you two seeking shelter from the rain?

755
00:43:21,371 --> 00:43:24,961
Ruoxi, why don't you tell me?

756
00:43:24,961 --> 00:43:26,912
With regards to officials who are corrupt and abuse the law,

757
00:43:26,912 --> 00:43:29,384
how should they be handled?

758
00:43:29,384 --> 00:43:31,123
I am just a palace maid,

759
00:43:31,123 --> 00:43:32,935
how would I know what should be done?

760
00:43:32,935 --> 00:43:35,010
13th Prince, please don't have a joke at my expense.

761
00:43:35,010 --> 00:43:36,603
Don't try to fool me.

762
00:43:36,603 --> 00:43:38,479
What is going on in your mind,

763
00:43:38,479 --> 00:43:41,315
I think I roughly know.

764
00:43:41,315 --> 00:43:43,337
Since ancient times the word "corruption"

765
00:43:43,337 --> 00:43:45,209
has always been followed by "abuse of the law."

766
00:43:45,209 --> 00:43:47,828
It's true that stealing the people's blood, sweat, and tears is abominable,

767
00:43:47,828 --> 00:43:49,128
but what is more detestable is

768
00:43:49,128 --> 00:43:50,503
abuse of the law.

769
00:43:50,503 --> 00:43:52,061
For the love of money,

770
00:43:52,061 --> 00:43:53,740
the people at the top and bottom collaborate with each other.

771
00:43:53,740 --> 00:43:56,076
Mutual cover-ups, no justice is upheld.

772
00:43:56,076 --> 00:43:58,291
This is even more harmful to human life.

773
00:43:58,291 --> 00:44:00,866
There will always be people using underhanded means to achieve their aims.

774
00:44:00,866 --> 00:44:03,167
Stop talking in circles, answer the question directly.

775
00:44:06,952 --> 00:44:08,761
Strict punishment with no leniency.

776
00:44:09,200 --> 00:44:11,642
A moment of tolerance leads to

777
00:44:11,642 --> 00:44:13,175
a rise in corruption.

778
00:44:13,720 --> 00:44:14,972
Poor governance

779
00:44:14,972 --> 00:44:16,890
is even more scary than corruption.

780
00:44:16,890 --> 00:44:18,608
If officials don't behave like officials,

781
00:44:18,608 --> 00:44:19,955
the ordinary people will have no way of making a living.

782
00:44:19,955 --> 00:44:22,645
Naturally, they won't behave like citizens anymore.

783
00:44:26,909 --> 00:44:28,500
If I said to you,

784
00:44:28,500 --> 00:44:30,195
the crime was committed by Ninth Brother,

785
00:44:30,960 --> 00:44:32,331
then what should be done?

786
00:44:33,887 --> 00:44:36,089
Then whatever needs to be done should be done.

787
00:44:36,089 --> 00:44:38,424
Do you really believe

788
00:44:38,424 --> 00:44:40,389
a prince should undergo the same punishment as a commoner?

789
00:44:41,380 --> 00:44:43,486
The money that was made legitimate by him should be returned.

790
00:44:43,486 --> 00:44:44,825
Punish him with a few beatings of the plank,

791
00:44:44,825 --> 00:44:46,651
so that he won't be able to get out of bed for six months.

792
00:44:46,651 --> 00:44:49,073
And then send him to the streets to be a beggar for three months.

793
00:44:49,073 --> 00:44:51,441
Let him experience how the poor have to get through their days.

794
00:44:51,441 --> 00:44:54,100
